"title": "8232: discipline, in the family",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8232",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Parents' loving, corrective training of their children, by verbal instruction and punishments, so that they grow up in the way God wants.</p>\n<h2>Parents are to discipline their children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:7\">HEB 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:5\">DEU 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:9-Heb12:11\">HEB 12:9–12:11</a></p>\n<h2>Parents discipline out of love for their children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:24\">PRO 13:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:12\">PRO 3:12</a></p>\n<h2>The means of parental discipline</h2>\n<h3>Training</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:6\">PRO 22:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:19\">GEN 18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:7\">DEU 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:17\">PRO 29:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:4\">EPH 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:21\">COL 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>Correction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:15\">PRO 22:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:18\">PRO 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:13-Prov23:14\">PRO 23:13–23:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:15\">PRO 29:15</a></p>\n<h3>Verbal instruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:4\">EPH 6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:9\">DEU 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:7\">DEU 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:20-Deut6:25\">DEU 6:20–6:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:19\">DEU 11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:13\">DEU 31:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:5\">PSA 78:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:8\">PRO 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:20\">PRO 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Punishment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:13-Prov23:14\">PRO 23:13–23:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:15\">PRO 22:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:15\">PRO 29:15</a></p>\n<h2>The purpose of parental discipline is to impart wisdom</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:15\">PRO 29:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:18\">PRO 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:15\">PRO 22:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:17\">PRO 29:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:9\">HEB 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:11\">HEB 12:11</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of parents who neglected discipline</h2>\n<h3>Eli</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:13\">1SA 3:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:5-1Kgs1:6\">1KI 1:5–1:6</a></strong></p>",
